# bwfilters

Simple whitelist/blacklist filter structures.


```python
from bwfilters import BWFilter

data = ['good', 'nice', 'bad']

my_filter = BWFilter()
my_filter.whitelist = ['good', 'nice']

my_filter.filter(lambda x: x, data)
>>> ['good', 'nice']
```


## Installation

```bash
pip install bwfilters
```



